data.description: ****ACTIVE UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER ACCEPTING BACK UP OFFERS ****This beautiful home boasts a finished basement, which is an exceptional feature in Spring Hill. With over 2700 square feet of living space, this home is perfect for those who value luxury and comfort. As you enter the home, you will be greeted by an elegant living room and dining room, perfect for entertaining guests. The dining room features a built-in cabinet/bar, while the home is adorned with beautiful plantation shutters. The kitchen is spacious, with plenty of counter space and cabinets for storage. It also has a window to the lanai, allowing natural light to flood in.The oversized master bathroom is a true oasis, complete with double vanities, a built-in cabinet, and a large walk-in closet. The remaining bedrooms are separated from the primary room, offering your guests the privacy they deserve.The stunning staircase leading to the finished basement is a work of art, and the possibilities for customization are endless. You can transform it into a game room, home theater, or even a home gym - the choice is yours!Step out onto the screened lanai and take in the large, privacy-fenced corner yard. It's the perfect spot to relax and enjoy the beautiful scenery. The yard also features an additional parking pad for convenience.This unique home is a rare find in Spring Hill, and it won't be on the market for long. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to make this house your new home!
